The paper deals with authentication and key distribution in IoT networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed approach also addresses energy efficiency, which is a concern in distributed computing (cs.DC) and system optimization (cs.SY). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques for security, which could potentially fall under the category of machine learning (cs.LG).
